<li id="cite_note-4"><b><a href="#cite_ref-4" title="">^</a></b> See, e.g., Lyons (2000), p. 36 ("RKO is usually cited as having produced the first true film noir, <i>Stranger on the Third Floor</i>"); Server (1998), p. 158 ("Often credited as the 'first' film noir"); Porfirio (1980), p. 269 ("the first true film noir").</li>
